MG_BOXES

Map Made By Kirby

CTs and Ts start with knives and they kill each other. As they kill each other, boxes will fall from the sky either yellow, orange or red. In each box it will contain a weapon with no clip ( No Ammo To Reload ).

The RED Box Will Contain a M4A1 - Spawns every 20 seconds

The ORANGE Box Will Contain a TMP - Spawns every 10 seconds

The YELLOW Box Will Contain a GLOCK - Spawns every 5 seconds

Texture Fixed
